Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community,
Having regard to Council Directive 91/689/EEC of 12 December 1991 on hazardous waste (1), as amended by Directive 94/31/EC (2), and in particular Article 8 (3) thereof,
Whereas the aforesaid provision requires the Commission to establish a format in which information is to be provided pursuant to Article 8 (3) of the Directive;
Whereas the Commission is assisted in this task by the Committee, composed of representatives of the Member States and chaired by the representative of the Commission, established pursuant to Article 18 of Council Directive 75/442/EEC of 15 July 1975 on waste (3), as last amended by Directive 91/692/EEC (4);
Whereas the measures envisaged by the Decision are in accordance with the opinion expressed by the abovementioned Committee,
